10         = 19\n| goals10        = 8\n| years11        = 2012\n| clubs11        = [[Deportivo Quito]]\n| caps11         = 10\n| goals11        = 3\n| years12        = 2012\u20132013\n| clubs12        = [[Deportivo T\u00e1chira F\u00fatbol Club|Deportivo T\u00e1chira]]\n| caps12         = 12\n| goals12        = 4\n| years13        = 2013\u20132014\n| clubs13        = [[Manta F\u00fatbol Club|Manta]]\n| caps13         = 42\n| goals13        = 10\n| years14        = 2014\u20132015\n| clubs14        = [[Club Sport Emelec|Emelec]]\n| caps14         = 54\n| goals14        = 12\n| years15        = 2016\u20132019\n| clubs15        = [[C.D. Universidad Cat\u00f3lica del Ecuador|Universidad Cat\u00f3lica]]\n| caps15         = 72\n| goals15        = 17\n| years16        = 2019\n| clubs16        = [[Deportivo Cuenca]]\n| caps16         = 6\n| goals16        = 1\n| years17        = 2020\u2013\n| clubs17        = [[S.D. Aucas|Aucas]]\n| caps17         = 0\n| goals17        = 0\n| nationalyears1 = \n| nationalteam1  = \n| nationalcaps1  =\n| nationalgoals1 = \n| medaltemplates =\n| pcupdate       = 21 March 2019\n| ntupdate       = \n}}\n\n'''Luis Miguel Escalada''' (born 27 February 1986) is an Argentine professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Forward (association football)|forward]] for [[S.D. Aucas|Aucas]].\n\n==Career==\nEscalada was born in [[Ceres, Santa Fe|Ceres]]. He has previously played for [[Boca Juniors]], [[Gimnasia y Esgrima de Jujuy|Gimnasia de Jujuy]] and [[Newell's Old Boys]] in Argentina, [[Club Sport Emelec|Emelec]] and [[Liga Deportiva Universitaria (Quito)|LDU Quito]] in [[Ecuador]], and [[Botafogo de Futebol e Regatas|Botafogo]] in [[Brazil]].\n\nEscalada signed with [[Major League Soccer]] side [[Real Salt Lake]] in early 2009 and made his MLS debut on 18 April 2009 as a substitute in a game against the [[New York Red Bulls]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mlsnet.com/scoreboard/game.jsp?match=04182009_RSLNY |title=Archived copy |accessdate=19 April 2009 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090422040058/http://web.mlsnet.com/scoreboard/game.jsp?match=04182009_RSLNY |archivedate=22 April 2009}}</ref> He scored his first goal on 25 April 2009 in a 6\u20130 win over [[New England Revolution]].\n\n==Career statistics==\n{{updated|13 March 2016}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Club\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Season\n!colspan=\"2\"|League\n!colspan=\"2\"|State League\n!colspan=\"2\"|Cup\n!colspan=\"2\"|Continental\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n|-\n!Apps\n!Goals\n!Apps\n!Goals\n!Apps\n!Goals\n!Apps\n!Goals\n!Apps\n!Goals\n|-\n|[[Club Atl\u00e9tico Boca Juniors|Boca Juniors]]\n|[[2004\u201305 Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n|2004-05]]\n|6||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||0||0||1||0||7||0\n|-\n|[[Club Sport Emelec|Emelec]]\n|[[2006 Campeonato Ecuatoriano de F\u00fatbol Serie A|2006]]\n|40||29||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||0||0||40||29\n|-\n|[[Liga Deportiva Universitaria de Quito|LDU Quito]]\n|[[2007 Campeonato Ecuatoriano de F\u00fatbol Serie A|2007]]\n|38||16||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||6||0||44||16\n|-\n|[[Botafogo de Futebol e Regatas|Botafogo]]\n|[[2008 Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie A|2008]]\n|0||0||2||0||0||0||0||0||2||0\n|-\n|[[Gimnasia y Esgrima de Jujuy|Gimnasia de Jujuy]]\n|[[2007\u201308 Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n|2007-08]]\n|11||2||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||0||0||0||0||11||2\n|-\n|[[Club Atl\u00e9tico Newell's Old Boys|Newell's Old Boys]]\n|[[2008\u201309 Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n|2008-09]]\n|0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||0||0||0||0||0||0\n|-\n|[[Real Salt Lake]]\n|[[2009 Major League Soccer season|2009]]\n|5||1||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||0||0||0||0||5||1\n|-\n|[[Club Deportivo Cuenca|Deportivo Cuenca]]\n|[[2010 Campeonato Ecuatoriano de F\u00fatbol Serie A|2010]]\n|40||16||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||6||2||46||18\n|-\n|[[Club Sporting Cristal|Sporting Cristal]]\n|[[2011 Torneo Descentralizado|2011]