ru]]\n[[Category:Argentine expatriate sportspeople in Venezuela]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Ecuador]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Brazil]]\n[[Category:Expatriate soccer players in the United States]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Peru]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Venezuela]]\n\n{{Argentina-footy-forward-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{short description|Argentine footballer|bot=PearBOT 5}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name           = Luis Miguel Escalada\n| image          = Emelec-Stron (5).jpg\n| caption        = Luis Miguel Escalada\n| full_name      = Luis Miguel Escalada with [[Club Sport Emelec|Emelec]] in February 2015\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1986|2|27|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = [[Ceres, Santa Fe|Ceres]], Argentina\n| height         = 5 ft 9 in\n| position       = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n| currentclub    = [[S.D. Aucas]]\n| clubnumber     = \n| youthyears1    = 2002\u20132004\n| youthclubs1    = [[Boca Juniors]]\n| years1         = 2004\u20132010\n| clubs1         = [[Boca Juniors]]\n| caps1          = 6  | goals1         = 0\n| years2         = 2006\n| clubs2         = [[Club Sport Emelec|Emelec]]\n| caps2          = 40 | goals2         = 29\n| years3         = 2007\u20132010\n| clubs3         = [[Liga Deportiva Universitaria de Quito|LDU Quito]]\n| caps3          = 38 | goals3         = 16\n| years4         = 2008\n| clubs4         = \u2192 [[Botafogo de Futebol e Regatas|Botafogo]] (loan)\n| caps4          = 2  | goals4         = 0\n| years5         = 2008\n| clubs5         = \u2192 [[Gimnasia y Esgrima de Jujuy|Gimnasia de Jujuy]] (loan)\n| caps5          = 11 | goals5         = 2\n| years6         = 2008\u20132009\n| clubs6         = \u2192 [[Newell's Old Boys]] (loan)\n| caps6          = 0  | goals6         = 0\n| years7         = 2009\n| clubs7         = \u2192 [[Real Salt Lake]] (loan)\n| caps7          = 5  | goals7         = 1\n| years8   