 [[Brazil]].\n\nEscalada signed with [[Major League Soccer]] side [[Real Salt Lake]] in early 2009 and made his MLS debut on 18 April 2009 as a substitute in a game against the [[New York Red Bulls]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.mlsnet.com/scoreboard/game.jsp?match=04182009_RSLNY |title=Archived copy |accessdate=19 April 2009 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090422040058/http://web.mlsnet.com/scoreboard/game.jsp?match=04182009_RSLNY |archivedate=22 April 2009}}</ref> He scored his first goal on 25 April 2009 in a 6\u20130 win over [[New England Revolution]].\n\n==Career statistics==\n{{updated|13 March 2016}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Club\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Season\n!colspan=\"2\"|League\n!colspan=\"2\"|State League\n!colspan=\"2\"|Cup\n!colspan=\"2\"|Continental\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n|-\n!Apps\n!Goals\n!Apps\n!Goals\n!Apps\n!Goals\n!Apps\n!Goals\n!Apps\n!Goals\n|-\n|[[Club Atl\u00e9tico Boca Juniors|Boca Juniors]]\n|[[2004\u201305 Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n|2004-05]]\n|6||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||0||0||1||0||7||0\n|-\n|[[Club Sport Emelec|Emelec]]\n|[[2006 Campeonato Ecuatoriano de F\u00fatbol Serie A|2006]]\n|40||29||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||0||0||40||29\n|-\n|[[Liga Deportiva Universitaria de Quito|LDU Quito]]\n|[[2007 Campeonato Ecuatoriano de F\u00fatbol Serie A|2007]]\n|38||16||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||6||0||44||16\n|-\n|[[Botafogo de Futebol e Regatas|Botafogo]]\n|[[2008 Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie A|2008]]\n|0||0||2||0||0||0||0||0||2||0\n|-\n|[[Gimnasia y Esgrima de Jujuy|Gimnasia de Jujuy]]\n|[[2007\u201308 Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n|2007-08]]\n|11||2||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||0||0||0||0||11||2\n|-\n|[[Club Atl\u00e9tico Newell's Old Boys|Newell's Old Boys]]\n|[[2008\u201309 Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n|2008-09]]\n|0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||0||0||0||0||0||0\n|-\n|[[Real Salt Lake]]\n|[[2009 Major League Soccer season|2009]]\n|5|